    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 16px;">Roster includes current and historical bankruptcy judges of the U.S. Bankruptcy Court for the Western District of Missouri, including senior status, retired, and deceased judges as recorded in CourtListener / Free Law Project judicial database.</p>
